= Dragon Warrior IV (NES) - Enemies =

This page documents the enemy data structure in Dragon Warrior IV for the NES, including monster stats, behaviors, and ROM locations.

'''Data Status:''' Monster data structure verified from Bank 6/7. Enemy type table at Bank 19 $b967.

